  <title>lcMatchingPair2</title>
  <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>lcMatchingPair2</keyword>&gt; element in an assessment interaction
    provides a table row with the pair of items that comprise a correct match in a matching
    interaction and, optionally, feedback on the pair or correct and incorrect matches. This element
    replaces the &lt;<keyword>lcMatchingPair</keyword>&gt; element in DITA 1.2.</shortdesc>
